  "title": "Warehouse Assistant / Storekeeper #81648",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: FMCG Wholesaler</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant / Storekeeper</strong></li><li>Working Location: West – Tuas (Company transport provided at Boon Lay MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday – Friday: 7.30 AM - 4.45 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT Pay + Allowances + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare packing materials; pack, unpack, and move goods carefully to prevent damage.</li><li>Get shipments ready for incoming and outgoing warehouse orders.</li><li>Receive, store, pick, pack, label, and prepare goods for delivery based on WMS work orders.</li><li>Help with stock control and meet quality standards for audit checks.</li><li>Keep the work area clean, safe, and neat; use space properly.</li><li>Report any missing items, damage, or stock differences found.</li><li>Follow service standards, work processes, rules, and regulations.</li><li>Follow SOPs and safety rules when handling goods and using warehouse equipment/vehicles.</li><li>Carry out other logistics tasks assigned by the Supervisor.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Basic understanding of English.</li><li>Willing to rotate duties (e.g., delivery support or labelling).</li><li>Able to work overtime when required.</li><li>Comfortable with lifting cartons (about 15kg) and standing for long periods.</li><li>Experience with handheld scanners and warehouse systems is an advantage.</li><li>Basic knowledge of equipment checks, and record-keeping is an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81648 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
